# HTTP headers applied by Cloudflare Workers' static-asset serving.
# Vite copies `public/_headers` verbatim into `dist/`, and Cloudflare
# Workers' assets pipeline reads it as a route → header map.
#
# `frame-ancestors` MUST be set as an HTTP header — the CSP spec
# explicitly disallows it from <meta http-equiv> tags. Without this
# header /embed could not be iframed cross-origin.

/embed
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://caveofcaerbannog.com https://*.caveofcaerbannog.com
  X-Frame-Options: ALLOW-FROM https://caveofcaerbannog.com

/embed.html
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://caveofcaerbannog.com https://*.caveofcaerbannog.com
  X-Frame-Options: ALLOW-FROM https://caveofcaerbannog.com
